In the light of that opinion, it is also necessary to review existing control systems so that they can operate with adequate efficiency and keep pace with the latest technologies.'
Brussels asked the independent scientific committee to investigate the problem in view of the prevalence of portable music players and the increasing number of young people exposed to noise caused by them.
