The judges of the Calabria Anti-Mafia Directorate have issued serious charges against the mayor and deputy mayor of Gioia Tauro, Giorgio Dal Torrione and Rosario Schiavone, and the mayor of Rosarno, Carlo Martelli, who were arrested this morning on charges of external participation in a criminal conspiracy.
